title: 关于BQ任务插件的报错
txt_content:
[13:21:13 WARN]: [BeautyQuests] An error occured while refreshing scoreboard line 3[13:21:13 WARN]: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: Account does not have this branch launched[13:21:13 WARN]:        at fr.skytasul.quests.structure.QuestBranch.getDescriptionLine(QuestBranch.java:91)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at fr.skytasul.quests.scoreboards.Scoreboard$Line.setLines(Scoreboard.java:249)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at fr.skytasul.quests.scoreboards.Scoreboard$Line.refreshLines(Scoreboard.java:227)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at fr.skytasul.quests.scoreboards.Scoreboard$1.run(Scoreboard.java:90)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at org.bukkit.craftbukkit.v1_12_R1.scheduler.CraftTask.run(CraftTask.java:76)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at org.bukkit.craftbukkit.v1_12_R1.scheduler.CraftAsyncTask.run(CraftAsyncTask.java:52)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor.runWorker(Unknown Source)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at java.util.concurrent.ThreadPoolExecutor$Worker.run(Unknown Source)[13:21:13 WARN]:        at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)
